{"tid":1548823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"How to get to the Airport?","createTime":"2019-09-07T06:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T11:52:30.000Z","uid":274161,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"36f6fa6788f5b42b9a273ecc742a3bf078c26115","tid":1548823,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:26:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Stay calm all the time as you are travelling</span></strong><br />\nPlease <strong>carry a bag with some clothes, and bring your passport and ticket</strong> as follows (<strong>No need to pay</strong>!! <a href=\"http://onward.flights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fonward.flights&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=d78144a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://onward.flights</a>):<br />\n<br />\nStep 1: fill your name as in your passport, and select departure (HKG) and arrival (<strong>SHORT TRIP!!</strong>), as well as date:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/DW6jTM0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDW6jTM0.png&h=c43d6f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStep 2: select flight<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/NXuaf0k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXuaf0k.png&h=30001b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStep 3: generate your ticket!<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/NXuaf0k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXuaf0k.png&h=30001b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS: It <strong>would be definitely working at bus-stops &amp; MRT stations</strong>, as the police can't verify the authenticity. <strong>But every one needs to be smart &amp; relaxed, as you are travelling</strong>"},{"pid":"797aa442d4a243bf4cf18faffdffc0391ea230c3","tid":1548823,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"071fbbf137ed6868dfd38b7d63f58b79c8e307d2","tid":1548823,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到<br />\n請大家幫手得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce42233efba64ed44fb931688f06bd0dabae988","tid":1548823,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"071fbbf137ed6868dfd38b7d63f58b79c8e307d2","tid":1548823,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到<br />\n請大家幫手得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"fcf1511838b128ba5864ec36aee2840647c989c0","tid":1548823,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bece4c263b34df6ebda0f2bee8ae40e9f3f826d7","tid":1548823,"uid":209367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"081fc987bb652207e490ad94c391521ed7fce92b","tid":1548823,"uid":209367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{