ed;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"40c93acbcae083df16b148ed1674c62a29933de6","tid":1548823,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904ea3aeefafe2600ba91cfcc9fe2f1726c69a71","tid":1548823,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0816b3160966347907157739ef285acf647f4727","tid":1548823,"uid":36115,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:37:23.000Z","msg":"唔好再教人偽造文書喇<br />\n揚撚曬班狗一睇就知係假啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭A車既話自己去澳門 佢都吹你唔漲<br />\n搭E車既話去東涌轉巴士去大澳昂坪都得<br />\n<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">整假機票係犯法</span></span><br />\n狗狗要check機票真定假好簡單<br />\n有你個booking reference或者機票號碼已經睇到係咪真係有呢張機票存在<br />\n如果佢一懷疑你 check到係冇就已經干犯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">偽造文書</span></span><br />\n即刻拉得你<br />\n<br />\n仲有巴打教人整假機票都要小心<br />\n有可能告你<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">教唆他人行使偽造文書</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家有千千萬萬個理由入大嶼山<br />\n唔使用d咁高風險既方法<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Mon Po狗死全家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:38:03.000Z","msg":"It would be definitely working at bus-stops &amp; MRT stations, as the police can't verify the authenticity. But every one needs to be smart &amp; relaxed, as you are travelling"},{"pid":"faf651a043fbd779eb4e14820a1c26e568ded32e","tid":1548823,"uid":266938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:42:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17aa0b8eac667c9c2b42d65c03fa63b5bec1d925","tid":1548823,"uid":36115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"904ea3aeefafe2600ba91cfc